name: A Stellar Voyage
description:
A picture that I captured and edited on my iPhone 11 a while back. The vivid light shafts leaking in through the renaissance inspired clouds is bound together by the glimmering starry scene, completing the cosmic x renaissance inspired delineation. 
This picture is also a humble reminder that fancy equipments and state of the art editing softwares aren't whats necessary to create an art piece that you can be proud of. To make the most out of our accessibilities is what artistic perseverance is all about!
